'''Asbestosis''' is a [[disease]] of the [[lung]]s caused by inhaling fibers of [[asbestos]]. It is not to be confused with [[mesothelioma]], a cancer of the lungs which is also caused by inhaling asbestos fibers. Asbestosis has been the subject of many [[lawsuit]]s, and many [[lawyer]]s specialize in asbestosis and mesothelioma.
